snippet.title: Geometry - Triangle Congruence (SSS, SAS)
snippet.description:
French math? Well, maybe not, but at least Im wearing a knitted beret. In this lesson, we introduce two rules that prove triangles congruent: SSS and SAS. Once we understand those, we complete two applicable proofs. Enjoy with your caviar, YAY MATH!
Please visit yaymath.org
